    "reveal_testimonials_G4MnAn": {
      "type": "reveal-testimonials",
      "blocks": {
        "testimonial_rRhnXK": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "quote",
            "text": "<p>Jessica Raftary</p><p><strong>Awesome 3-Wheel Bike</strong><br/>Easy to pedal and smooth ride. I look forward to many fun adventures as I go on bike rides while camping. The 3 wheel bike is easy to fold and transport. I love the stability I feel while riding.<br/><br/></p>",
            "author": "",
            "author_info": "",
            "author_url": "shopify://products/triker-folding-3-wheels-electric-bike",
            "image_ratio": "adapt",
            "highlighted_text": "none",
            "highlighted_scribble": "circle"
          }
        },
        "testimonial_eXYpab": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "quote",
            "text": "<p>Bojack Call</p><p>Daughters first e-bike<br/>Bought the white one for my daughter and wife bought the black one. They have put 40 miles on it already. The bike is a lot lighter than my ebike which made it more power and if you do run out of battery it pedals like a regular bike with ease. Would highly recommend, alot of features for the price.<br/></p><p><br/><br/></p>",
            "author": "",
            "author_info": "",
            "author_url": "shopify://products/cityone-2-0-commute-electric-bike",
            "image_ratio": "adapt",
            "highlighted_text": "none",
            "highlighted_scribble": "circle"
          }
        },
        "testimonial_YyMmpW": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "quote",
            "text": "<p>Keith A. Valdez</p><p>Absolutely great bike! <br/>Fantastic ride, easy to put together and easier to ride! The charger/battery doesn't directly indicate that it's charging but the charging cable does change color to indicate charging and fully charged. The size of the bike is very satisfying. It feels very durable. It was a great price. a really amazing deal! :)</p>",
            "author": "",
            "author_info": "",
            "author_url": "shopify://products/qlife-racer-fat-tire-electric-bike",
            "image_ratio": "adapt",
            "highlighted_text": "none",
            "highlighted_scribble": "circle"
          }
        },
        "testimonial_Cyrq68": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "quote",
            "text": "<p>Kimberly</p><p>Great purchase!<br/>My wife and I bought these bikes as they were the most affordable electric bikes we could find. We were really impressed with the peddle assist and speed. We've ridden the bikes about 4 times now and really enjoy them. The only thing we changed was the seats. We bought more padded seats to make longer rides more enjoyable. Overall we are happy with the purchase.<br/><br/><br/></p>",
            "author": "",
            "author_info": "",
            "author_url": "shopify://products/cityone-2-0-mountain-electric-bike",
            "image_ratio": "adapt",
            "highlighted_text": "none",
            "highlighted_scribble": "circle"
          }
        },
        "testimonial_ad4FtM": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "quote",
            "text": "<p>Ehlay</p><p>Amazing product! Perfect for everyday use<br/>Absolutely love this bike. The top speed is 28+Mph. Would definitely recommend for anybody wanting to trail ride, or just cruising around town! The horn is very loud.Overall I’ve been riding this bike for about 2 and a half weeks and have been very happy with it. Would 100% buy again.<br/></p>",
            "author": "",
            "author_info": "",
            "author_url": "shopify://products/spark-moped-style-e-bike",
            "image_ratio": "adapt",
            "highlighted_text": "none",
            "highlighted_scribble": "circle"
          }
        }
      },
